### 1. GET all courses
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Courses

### 2. GET all students
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Students

### 3. GET all enrollments
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Enrollments

### 4. GET courses filtered by department
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Courses?$filter=departmentCode eq 'CS'

### 5. GET courses filtered by semester
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Courses?$filter=semester eq 1

### 6. GET students with CGPA above 8.0
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Students?$filter=cgpa gt 8.0

### 7. GET courses where seats available
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Courses?$filter=currentEnrolled lt maxStudents

### 8. GET all enrollments for a specific student
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Enrollments?$filter=studentId eq 'S01'

### 9. POST new student enrollment
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Enrollments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "S07",
  "courseCode": "CS101",
  "enrollmentDate": "2024-01-15",
  "status": "Enrolled",
  "attendancePercent": 0
}

### 10. PATCH enrollment to add grade
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Enrollments(studentId='S03',courseCode='EC201')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grade": "A",
  "gradePoints": 10,
  "status": "Completed"
}

### 11. GET students sorted by CGPA descending
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Students?$orderby=cgpa desc

### 12. GET courses with select fields
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Courses?$select=code,title,credits,semester

### 13. GET top 5 students
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/university/Students?$top=5